name: Influx of Unfamiliar Feelings
description:
I remember there was a time when I
was confronted by a harsh truth and it
raised a lot of emotions that I wasn’t
prepared for. There are just some
truths that will paralyse you, now
matter how well you’ve handled
difficult situations in the past. I
remember wanting to be alone. I didn’t
want anyone to see me confront it. ||
Created in Cinema 4d, Octane and
Photoshop || 3858px?×?5456px || Mark
Constantine Inducil 2021
